                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">For what it's worth, on a North Ro normal adventure (65) I parsed the animation to be 30 DPS when buffed with NDT and SoV.  
<br />

<br />
The pet of a level 65 Necro (buffed by the necro) came to 40 DPS from my logs.  
<br />

<br />
Animations are good free damage, they just have very few hps.
<br />

<br />
For reference, the warrior that I group with routinely comes out at around 60 DPS versus these same mobs when using a Great Staff of Thunder and buffed with SoV and NDT.</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
